review_blob: This is a great beer for long drinking sessions. Much less filling than the lager and the taste has much less edge, so it goes down faster too.  On occasion Ill grab a case of this if Im going to a party.

This is my favorite beer, personally I compare everything else I drink to it. For me, this is the beer to sit down and decompress from a long day to. Drinks smooth with a unique taste that is not overpowering. Not always the best choice for all situations, but most often chosen over any other.
